@Devices.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080
@ApiVersion = 1
@DeviceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Health - Liveness
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Health - Readiness (includes DB check)
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Create device
POST {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
	"name": "Edge Router",
	"brand": "Fabrikam",
	"state": "available"
}

###

### Get all devices (paged)
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Get device by id
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/{{DeviceId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get devices by brand
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/brand/Fabrikam
Accept: application/json

###

### Get devices by state
GET {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/state/available
Accept: application/json

###

### Full update device
PUT {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/{{DeviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
	"name": "Edge Router X",
	"brand": "Fabrikam",
	"state": "inactive"
}

###

### Partial update device
PATCH {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/{{DeviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
	"state": "in-use"
}

###

### Delete device
DELETE {{Devices.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/devices/{{DeviceId}}
Accept: application/json

###
